  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_9",
    "text": "荇菜属有数个原品种，外形差异不。有景观效果类似的同属植物银莲 花（N.indica）、水莲（N.cristatum）等，花为白色，叶形与荇菜差异不大。 有景观效果近似的不同科属品种—莼菜（Braseniaschreberi），叶为椭圆形， 与荇菜叶形有区别，花较，红褐。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06576980568011959,
      0.8642487046632125,
      0.6915794718485302,
      0.9333333333333333
    ],
    "page": "docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_docstructbench_dianzishu_zhongwenzaixian-o.O-61510863.pdf_73_11",
    "text": "荇菜叶翠绿，小黄花密集， 精巧别致，是优良的小型浮叶 景观植物。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
